item.title: CVE-2020-4983|2024-08-04T08:22:08.392Z -- ibm -- spectrum%20lsf%20suite
item.description: IBM Spectrum LSF 10.1 and IBM Spectrum LSF Suite 10.2 could allow a user on the local network who has privileges to submit LSF jobs to execute arbitrary commands. IBM X-Force ID: 192586.
